{"tid":2231564,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"輸打贏要】社工阻差辦公罪脫　律政司再引例上訴","createTime":"2020-10-05T17:47:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T22:11:46.000Z","uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"97a1b95cc81ab8d8d101e3f3bc1e7c4fa810cfa7","tid":2231564,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T17:47:04.000Z","msg":"【<br />\n<br />\n去年8月25日「荃葵青大遊行」期間，一名女社工遭警截查，要求女督察出示委任證不果，反被指控阻差辦公，早前在西九龍裁判法院獲判「阻差辦公」及「未能在規定下出示身分證明文件」兩罪不成立，律政司已根據《裁判官條例》第105條以案件呈述的方式提出上訴。<br />\n<br />\n社工林曉樺（22歲）早前被控於去年8月25日在荃灣阻撓女督察梁敏儀執行職務，控方於開審前新增一項交替控罪「未能在規定下出示身分證明文件」。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官黃雅茵裁決時指，根據《警察通例》，除非特殊情况，警員單是穿著制服，絕非不出示委任證的理由。女督察在庭上稱注意不到被告已拿出身份證，但片段顯示 43 秒內取出身份證屬合理時間。黃官遂判兩項控罪均不成立，控方須付堂費。<br />\n<br />\n律政司回覆傳媒查詢，表示由於司法程序仍在進行，不適宜進一步評論。<br />\n<br />\n資料圖片來源︰網上<br />\n========================= <br />\n🚚丘品購物網站正式上線啦「丘MART」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.yaumart.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.yaumart.com%2F&d=SBcu0iNh8WN0EYdC3CIZL9%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=f98e5374\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.yaumart.com/</a> <br />\n========================= <br />\n感謝讀者支持 支持新聞部課金方法 <br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3579Rub\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3579Rub&d=SBcu0iNh8WN0EYdC3CIZL9%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=e6589780\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3579Rub</a> <br />\n=========================<br />\n丘品已經登陸Patreon 歡迎成為會員&rdquo;搶先收睇 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/cupidproducer\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2Fcupidproducer&d=SBcu0iNh8WN0EYdC3CIZL9%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=25037f58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.patreon.com/cupidproducer</a><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash; <br />\n📣Instagram : <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2LShtZr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2